00:06:49.600 --> 00:06:53.410
Oh, no! What am I going to tell Takumi?!

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:57.580
Takumi!

00:06:57.580 --> 00:07:00.950
What are you all panicked about?

00:07:00.950 --> 00:07:03.380
Never mind that.

00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:09.120
Say, if you're free this Saturday,
you want to go racing at Mt. Akina?

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:11.290
--No.
--Why not?

00:07:11.290 --> 00:07:16.900
Sorry, but I don't drive a car
unless it's absolutely necessary.

00:07:16.900 --> 00:07:18.200
Takumi!

00:07:18.200 --> 00:07:21.640
