00:07:21.640 --> 00:07:23.540
Okay.

00:07:23.540 --> 00:07:26.010
Hey!

00:07:26.010 --> 00:07:29.710
Not good. This is not good.

00:07:29.710 --> 00:07:32.250
See you tomorrow.

00:07:32.250 --> 00:07:35.020
Hey, Takumi.

