were to challenge you to a race.

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:46.030
You'd accept, of course, right?

00:07:46.030 --> 00:07:48.500
No way. I'm not into that scene.

00:07:48.500 --> 00:07:50.570
What?! Don't say that!

00:07:50.570 --> 00:07:52.230
What's it matter to you?

00:07:52.230 --> 00:07:56.340
Um... well... uh... That's beside the point.

00:07:56.340 --> 00:07:59.210
