I couldn't help but pretend to be
a member of the Speed Stars...

00:10:04.330 --> 00:10:06.730
...and before I knew what was happening...

00:10:06.730 --> 00:10:09.600
...he had already issued
the challenge and driven off.

00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:13.510
Why didn't you tell us about this before?!

00:10:13.510 --> 00:10:18.110
I was going to tell you, I swear.
I was just waiting for the right moment.

00:10:18.110 --> 00:10:21.550
Takumi, I'm sorry. I messed up.

00:10:21.550 --> 00:10:24.350
Please forgive me!

